Name: Sex Adventures - Futanari Doctor

Visual Novel Description Miyu, a beautiful young woman, goes desperately to the doctor with an embarrassing problem. She complains that whatever she’s doing, she just can’t have an orgasm. After a series of intimate questions, the doctor still fails to establish a diagnosis. She then asks her patient to lie on her back and undress for a physical consultation. Everything seems alright, but that doesn’t help the sexually frustrated girl. The situation takes a turn when the doctor asks her if she agrees with a different treatment. Miyu is certainly not ready for what is to come.
